author: ringstrom
msg: Execute the user supplied diff3 with full environment because it's not
possible to use an X11 program without it, and also for consistency
with how a user supplied diff is executed.
* subversion/libsvn_subr/io.c
(svn_io_run_diff3): Tell svn_io_run_cmd to keep the environment.

author: ringstrom
msg: Fix issue 1914 - svn_wc__run_log ignoring external diff3 binary.
Use the internal diff3 when running the dry merge to present the
status to the user, and use the user supplied diff3 when running the
real merge.
Patch contributed by Marc Haesen.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/update_editor.c
(close_directory): Supply the user's diff3 to svn_wc__run_log.
(install_file): Use the internal diff3.
